&nbsp;given to&nbsp;the festival&rsquo;s own productions, the immersive the performances which attract high attention of&nbsp;professional community.</p></div><div class="col-md-6"> <div class="fotorama" data-nav="false" data-loop="true" data-autoplay="true" data-arrows="false" data-transition="crossfade" data-allowfullscreen="true" data-stopautoplayontouch="false"> <img src="/img/Galery/1-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/2-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/3-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/4-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/5-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/6-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/8-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/9-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/10-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/11-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/12-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/13-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/14-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/15-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/16-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/17-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/18-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точка доступа "> <img src="/img/Galery/19-min.png?v1 " alt="The Point of Access "" alt="Точка доступа"> <img src="/img/Galery/20-min.png?v1" alt="The Point of Access" " alt="Точ